1
00:26:14,407 --> 00:26:16,784
My name is Loki.

2
00:26:16,993 --> 00:26:20,329
We are agents
of the Time Variance Authority.

3
00:26:21,289 --> 00:26:24,500
I bring you all dark tidings.

4
00:26:24,959 --> 00:26:26,878
All of you!

5
00:26:27,378 --> 00:26:29,839
You're all about to die.

6
00:26:29,922 --> 00:26:36,554
That volcano is about to erupt!

7
00:26:38,431 --> 00:26:43,019
I would know, because I'm from the future.

